#: ../../C/chad-box.rst:5
msgid "chad box"
msgstr "chad box"

#: ../../C/chad-box.rst:7
msgid "n\\."
msgstr "名詞"

#: ../../C/chad-box.rst:9
msgid ""
"A metal box about the size of a lunchbox (or in some models a large "
"wastebasket), for collecting the :ref:`chad` (sense 2) that accumulated in "
":ref:`Iron-Age` card punches. You had to open the covers of the card punch "
"periodically and empty the chad box. The :ref:`bit-bucket` was notionally "
"the equivalent device in the CPU enclosure, which was typically across the "
"room in another great gray-and-blue box."
msgstr ""
"\\ :ref:`Iron-Age`\\ のカードパンチにたまった\\ :ref:`chad`\\ "
"(語義2)を集めるための、弁当箱ほどの大きさ(一部のモデルでは大きなくず入れほど)の金属箱。カードパンチのカバーを定期的に開けてchad "
"boxを空にしなければなりませんでした。\\ :ref:`bit-bucket`\\ "
"は、CPU筐体内の概念上の等価デバイスでした。それは通常、部屋の向こう側の別の巨大な灰色と青の箱の中にありました。"
